==English==
===Verb===
'''to [[beat]] [[around]] [[the]] [[bush]]'''
#{{idiom}} To [[treat]] a topic but [[omit]] its main [[points]], often [[intentionally]]; to [[delay]] or [[avoid]] talking about something difficult or unpleasant.
#:''Please stop '''beating around the bush''' and tell me what the problem is!''

